location of the frosted glass window glass relative to other objects.  to locate the frosted glass window glass, start by identifying the parapet, which is positioned below the window glass. then, locate the fridge, which is positioned to the left of the window glass. finally, find the radiator, which is positioned below and slightly to the right of the window glass.  follow these relative directions to locate the frosted glass window glass in the scene.

6s7QHgap2fW.basis.glb_microwave.lang_desc: microwave, which is a built-in microwave oven. it is located in the kitchen cabinet towards the right side of the frame. to locate it, start by identifying the kitchen cabinet positioned slightly above the countertop on the left side. the microwave can be found within the kitchen cabinet, positioned towards the right side.
